@{
    Layout = null;
}
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - BelieveIn</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            /* Sunset Gradient Background */
            /* Optimized Sunset Gradient for your Logo */
            background: linear-gradient( 180deg, #FFE082 0%, #FFB74D 50%, #FF7043 100% );
            background-attachment: fixed; /* Keeps background still while scrolling */
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            color: black;
        }

        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
            backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(15px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
            border-radius: 20px;
            padding: 40px;
            max-width: 700px;
            margin: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 32px 0 rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.37);
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
            color: darkorange;
            text-shadow: 2px 2px 4px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
        }

        h2 {
            color: black;
            margin-top: 25px;
            border-left: 4px solid #f27121;
            padding-left: 10px;
        }

        p {
            line-height: 1.7;
            color: black;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }

        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            opacity: 0.7;
            text-align: center;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="glass-card">
        <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
        <p>Your trust is the foundation of <strong>BelieveIn</strong>. This policy details our commitment to protecting your data.</p>

        <h2>1. Data Collection</h2>
        <p>Through Google or Facebook login, we access your name and email to identify you. We do not access private files, friends, or social feeds.</p>

        <h2>2. Data Usage</h2>
        <p>Your data stays with us. We use it only for authentication. We never sell your personal information to third parties.</p>

        <h2>3. Security</h2>
        <p>Just like the sunset remains constant, we consistently monitor our systems to ensure your data remains encrypted and safe.</p>

        <h2>4. Contact</h2>
        <p>Questions? Reach out at: <br><strong>getbelievein@gmail.com</strong></p>

        <div class="footer">&copy; @DateTime.UtcNow.Year BelieveIn</div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>